================================================================================
  DomotiCharts
================================================================================

About DomotiCharts:
-------------
DomotiCharts is a wrapper around googles HighCharts to generate nice charts from DomotiGa devices.
The graphs are based on the logged status changes.


Requirements:
-------------
To be able to view a chart the following parts needs to 
- Enable the "Log status changes to db" option in the "Edit Device value" form.
- At the Graphs page select the correct "gauge" or "counter" type


How to install 'DomotiCharts':
-------------------
Unpack the directory to /var/www, or put it's contents in the webroot.
Change the connection details to connect to the DomotiGa database in the 'config.php'

open in the browser the index.php page. When everything is ok, it should show the list of graphs to view
